description:
Free Princess Dress Up Designer Prom Party Games is a fun game where you have to dress up Girls Models different dress.

Change all kinds of shirts, dresses, skirts, boots, and wings! Then you can even dazzle things up with jewelry! It's a total fashion makeover!

It's like your own dress where you can create the styles that make the other girls! Now you can design your own 'Princess Designer Prom Party' like never before!
